            "summary": "What type of AI? In my Specialization, I have created a squad&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<h1 class=\"align-center\">What type of AI?</h1>\n<p> </p>\n<p>In my Specialization, I have created a squad that works together to win against the player. There are four types of AI: Medic, Leader, Decoy, and Flanker, each with their own role to play.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<table class=\"align-center\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 560px; height: 350px;\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 50.3594px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 100%; height: 50%;\"><figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/9/Leader.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/9/responsive/Leader-xs.png 300w ,https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/9/responsive/Leader-sm.png 480w ,https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/9/responsive/Leader-md.png 768w ,https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/9/responsive/Leader-lg.png 1024w\"></figure></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 50.3594px;\">\n<td class=\"align-center\" style=\"width: 100%;\"><strong>Leader</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 50.3594px;\">\n<td class=\"align-center\" style=\"width: 100%;\">The Leader holds the team together</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table class=\"align-center\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 560px; height: 350px;\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 50.3594px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\" scope=\"colgroup\"><figure class=\"post__image post__image--center\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/9/Medic.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/9/responsive/Medic-xs.png 300w ,https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/9/responsive/Medic-sm.png 480w ,https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/9/responsive/Medic-md.png 768w ,https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/9/responsive/Medic-lg.png 1024w\"></figure></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 50.3594px;\">\n<td class=\"align-center\" style=\"width: 100%;\"><strong>Medic</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 50.3594px;\">\n<td class=\"align-center\" style=\"width: 100%;\">The Medic focuses on keeping his teammates alive</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table class=\" align-center\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 560px; height: 350px; border-style: none;\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 50.3594px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\"><figure class=\"post__image post__image--center\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/9/Decoy.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/9/responsive/Decoy-xs.png 300w ,https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/9/responsive/Decoy-sm.png 480w ,https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/9/responsive/Decoy-md.png 768w ,https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/9/responsive/Decoy-lg.png 1024w\"></figure></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 50.3594px;\">\n<td class=\"align-center\" style=\"width: 100%;\"><strong>Decoy</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 50.3594px;\">\n<td class=\"align-center\" style=\"width: 100%;\">The Decoy distracts and diverts the player's attention</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table class=\"align-center\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 560px; height: 350px; border-style: none;\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 76px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 100%; height: 76px;\"><figure class=\"post__image post__image--center\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/9/Flanker.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/9/responsive/Flanker-xs.png 300w ,https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/9/responsive/Flanker-sm.png 480w ,https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/9/responsive/Flanker-md.png 768w ,https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/9/responsive/Flanker-lg.png 1024w\"></figure></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 50.3594px;\">\n<td class=\"align-center\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 50.3594px;\"><strong>Flanker</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 107.953px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 100%; height: 107.953px;\">The Flanker sneaks behind the player to attack from behind</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>",
