            "id": "https://newmaddog.github.io/project-6-eternal-night-3.html",
            "url": "https://newmaddog.github.io/project-6-eternal-night-3.html",
            "title": "Project 6 :Eternal Night",
            "summary": "Summary In a world plunged into darkness by the insatiable appetite of&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"summary\" class=\"align-center\">Summary</h2>\n<p><em>In a world plunged into darkness by the insatiable appetite of an ancient malevolent deity that devours the sun, our protagonist embarks on an epic adventure to restore light to the realm. With courage as her guiding light, she traverses treacherous lands, confronting formidable adversaries and overcoming daunting challenges in her quest to reclaim the stolen sun.</em></p>\n<figure class=\"post__image post__image--center\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/6/Skaermbild-2024-03-29-161305.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"943\" height=\"530\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/6/responsive/Skaermbild-2024-03-29-161305-xs.png 300w ,https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/6/responsive/Skaermbild-2024-03-29-161305-sm.png 480w ,https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/6/responsive/Skaermbild-2024-03-29-161305-md.png 768w ,https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/6/responsive/Skaermbild-2024-03-29-161305-lg.png 1024w\"></figure>\n<h2 id=\"contribution\" class=\"align-center\">Contribution</h2>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>",
