        {
            "id": "https://newmaddog.github.io/test.html",
            "url": "https://newmaddog.github.io/test.html",
            "title": "About Me",
            "summary": "Who am I? Hey, I'm Erico Leonardo Alexander Pizarro Gutierrez, and I'm&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<figure class=\"post__image post__image--left\"><span style=\"color: var(--headings-color); font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  style=\"outline: 3px solid rgba(var(--color-primary-rgb), 0.55) !important;\" src=\"https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/2/sp22ericopizarrogutierrez-340x425.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"340\" height=\"425\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/2/responsive/sp22ericopizarrogutierrez-340x425-xs.png 300w ,https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/2/responsive/sp22ericopizarrogutierrez-340x425-sm.png 480w ,https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/2/responsive/sp22ericopizarrogutierrez-340x425-md.png 768w ,https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/2/responsive/sp22ericopizarrogutierrez-340x425-lg.png 1024w\"></figure></span></p>\n<p><strong>Who am I?</strong></p>\n<p class=\"align-left\"><em>Hey, I'm Erico Leonardo Alexander Pizarro Gutierrez, and I'm into game programming. Currently, I'm studying at The Game Assembly, getting the hang of C++ language. Just trying to up my game and make some cool stuff!</em></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"align-center\"><strong>Hobby</strong></p>\n<p class=\"align-left\"><em>I possess a diverse range of interests, yet among them, I derive the greatest enjoyment from engaging in video games. Specifically, I find myself particularly drawn to titles such as League of Legends, Tekken 7 and 8, Street Fighter 6, and Battlefield. These genres of games captivate me the most, offering immersive experiences that allow me to indulge in strategic gameplay, thrilling combat encounters, and the adrenaline rush of competitive action.</em></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"align-center\"><strong>What I did on TGA</strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<figure class=\"post__image post__image--center\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EIH1gDV8pJI\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/2/Skaermbild-2024-03-29-164555-3-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"311\" height=\"175\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/2/responsive/Skaermbild-2024-03-29-164555-3-2-xs.png 300w ,https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/2/responsive/Skaermbild-2024-03-29-164555-3-2-sm.png 480w ,https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/2/responsive/Skaermbild-2024-03-29-164555-3-2-md.png 768w ,https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/2/responsive/Skaermbild-2024-03-29-164555-3-2-lg.png 1024w\"></figure></a></p>\n<p class=\"align-center\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><em>Game Project1: Viking Rush</em></span></strong></p>\n<figure class=\"post__image post__image--center\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=twI3MUjhN4k\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/2/ComingSoon-3-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"311\" height=\"150\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/2/responsive/ComingSoon-3-2-xs.png 300w ,https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/2/responsive/ComingSoon-3-2-sm.png 480w ,https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/2/responsive/ComingSoon-3-2-md.png 768w ,https://newmaddog.github.io/media/posts/2/responsive/ComingSoon-3-2-lg.png 1024w\"></figure></a></p>\n<figure class=\"post__image post__image--center\"><strong><em><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Game Project2: Catdow<em style=\"color: var(--text-primary-color); font-family: var(--editor-font-family); font-size: inherit; font-weight: var(--font-weight-normal);\"> <br></em><br></span></em></strong><strong><em style=\"color: var(--text-primary-color); font-family: var(--editor-font-family); font-size: inherit; font-weight: var(--font-weight-normal);\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_ZovHQnOLtY\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"